graph LR
    KServe[KServe Platform]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KServe -->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager 1.x<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Serverless Mode)
    KServe -->|serverless autoscaling<br/>revision management| Knative[Knative Serving 1.x<br/>OPTIONAL - Serverless mode]
    KServe -->|traffic management<br/>VirtualServices<br/>DestinationRules<br/>mTLS| Istio[Istio 1.x / OSSM<br/>OPTIONAL - Recommended]

    %% External Dependencies (Advanced Features)
    KServe -.->|custom metric autoscaling<br/>raw deployment mode| KEDA[KEDA 2.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KServe -.->|metrics collection<br/>export| OTelOperator[OpenTelemetry Operator<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KServe -.->|ServiceMonitor<br/>PodMonitor| PrometheusOperator[Prometheus Operator<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KServe -.->|alternative ingress<br/>Gateway API| GatewayAPI[Gateway API 1.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KServe -.->|multi-node LLM<br/>distributed inference| LeaderWorkerSet[LeaderWorkerSet 1.x<br/>OPTIONAL - LLM only]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies (Integration)
    KServe -->|VirtualServices<br/>PeerAuthentication<br/>AuthorizationPolicy| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - OSSM<br/>INTERNAL - Traffic mgmt]
    KServe -->|external exposure<br/>Routes| OpenShiftRoutes[OpenShift Routes<br/>INTERNAL]
    KServe -.->|UI management<br/>API calls| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>INTERNAL]
    KServe -.->|metrics authentication<br/>OAuth Proxy| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>INTERNAL]
    KServe -.->|model metadata<br/>versioning| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>INTERNAL]
    KServe -.->|model artifacts<br/>MLflow integration| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>INTERNAL]
    KServe -.->|external authz<br/>AuthorizationPolicy| Authorino[Authorino<br/>INTERNAL - Optional]

    %% External Services (Storage)
    KServe -->|model artifacts<br/>download| S3[S3 Storage<br/>AWS S3 / MinIO / Ceph<br/>EXTERNAL]
    KServe -.->|model artifacts<br/>download| GCS[Google Cloud Storage<br/>EXTERNAL]
    KServe -.->|model artifacts<br/>download| Azure[Azure Blob Storage<br/>EXTERNAL]

    %% Core Kubernetes
    KServe -->|resource management<br/>CR watch/create| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>CORE]

    %% Eventing (Optional)
    KServe -.->|request/response logging<br/>events| KnativeEventing[Knative Eventing<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Integration Points (Reverse Dependencies)
    Dashboard -.->|creates InferenceService| KServe
    Pipelines -.->|auto-deploy models| KServe

